Holy cow! Michael, you have come up with such richly funny and phenomenally entertaining things on your show. I discovered you several or more months ago, and so very glad I did.


Oh my goodness.
That show where you had videoed the karaoke singers from the various pubs singing Gary Barlow songs had me in stitches!!! I've seen it now about four or so times...great! "Don't forget me bag! Now dance!"


These 'Send to All' portions are so funny and entertaining as well! This one with Sharon and Ozzie trying to face time her was hilarious...as were the replies from her phone.
